WEBVTT

1
00:05:57.524 --> 00:06:01.236
Lower your weapon.

2
00:07:25.320 --> 00:07:27.948
The DEA didn't get lucky.

3
00:07:28.031 --> 00:07:29.241
There's a rat!

4
00:07:30.450 --> 00:07:32.494
And Benito will get rid of it!

5
00:14:02.676 --> 00:14:06.763
It seems that we have
a very big problem.

6
00:14:06.846 --> 00:14:08.265
In this house.

7
00:14:09.933 --> 00:14:13.853
And it seems
we have an infestation...

8
00:14:28.785 --> 00:14:30.704
...about our tunnel.

9
00:14:31.663 --> 00:14:33.498
And they stole our cheese.

10
00:14:40.463 --> 00:14:42.257
Vasquez killed a pig for me.

11
00:14:46.636 --> 00:14:48.680
But all you idiots...

12
00:14:49.931 --> 00:14:52.392
How many rats are there here?

13
00:14:55.562 --> 00:14:57.522
Who's the rat. <i>cabrones?</i>

14
00:15:06.281 --> 00:15:08.199
Was it you. my friend?

15
00:15:08.950 --> 00:15:10.452
Are you the rat?

16
00:15:10.535 --> 00:15:13.038
No. boss. No. never.

17
00:15:17.042 --> 00:15:18.918
Kill him.

18
00:15:20.128 --> 00:15:22.047
I know he's your cousin.

19
00:15:23.006 --> 00:15:25.550
I gave you
your first job together. remember?

20
00:15:25.634 --> 00:15:27.093
When you were kids.

21
00:15:41.274 --> 00:15:43.526
No. cousin. don't kill me.

22
00:15:43.610 --> 00:15:45.320
Don't kill me.

23
00:15:52.952 --> 00:15:57.290
If we find the rats.
they'll lead us to the pigs!

24
00:16:04.506 --> 00:16:05.965
Quite a performance.

25
00:16:07.509 --> 00:16:10.345
-He's improved. no?
-No. he hasn't.

26
00:16:14.891 --> 00:16:16.976
He's survived much worse.

27
00:16:18.395 --> 00:16:20.230
Looks like you need the help.

28
00:16:20.313 --> 00:16:22.607
You're helping in El Paso.

29
00:16:24.651 --> 00:16:26.111
Months of work for nothing.

30
00:16:27.946 --> 00:16:29.239
Flush out the rats.

31
00:16:30.448 --> 00:16:32.575
Papito operated like a shadow.

32
00:16:33.743 --> 00:16:36.329
The work you're doing there is vital.

33
00:18:35.323 --> 00:18:38.243
Hi. I'm here
to collect the order. Thanks.

34
00:19:16.948 --> 00:19:20.118
-Appreciate it. thanks.
-Thanks.

35
00:28:37.967 --> 00:28:40.302
Hi. I'm here for the order.

36
00:29:42.948 --> 00:29:46.869
Hey. look at you. buddy.
You're a lucky man.

37
00:35:01.058 --> 00:35:02.392
What's going on?

38
00:36:47.623 --> 00:36:51.376
Calm down.
There's no reason to panic.

39
00:36:53.629 --> 00:36:58.759
Vasquez will keep his mouth shut.
He'll do time in prison. Besides...

40
00:37:01.386 --> 00:37:03.055
-There was barely any money.
-Shit.

41
00:37:04.640 --> 00:37:08.310
This makes us look weak!
First the tunnel. then this! It's...

42
00:37:08.393 --> 00:37:10.062
Open season on us.

43
00:37:12.689 --> 00:37:15.651
This happened in your city. didn't it?

44
00:37:35.504 --> 00:37:38.006
<i>These bastards aren't civilians.</i>

45
00:37:38.090 --> 00:37:40.342
Military grade. Very strange.

46
00:37:43.762 --> 00:37:47.307
They're going rogue.
They lost their informant. their friend.

47
00:37:47.391 --> 00:37:50.852
and they're out for revenge.
that's it.

48
00:45:10.708 --> 00:45:12.419
Fuck you!

49
00:48:44.380 --> 00:48:46.257
Who the hell is doing this?!

50
00:48:46.341 --> 00:48:48.343
How come you haven't found them?
Tell me!

51
00:48:50.345 --> 00:48:53.348
<i>I have to start everything
from scratch. rebuild everything.</i>

52
00:48:54.974 --> 00:48:57.602
It's the DEA pigs.

53
00:48:57.685 --> 00:49:00.146
They're making fun of us!

54
00:49:01.648 --> 00:49:06.861
I'm sure. I'm sure they're laughing at us.
I'm sure it's them!

55
00:49:06.944 --> 00:49:08.488
The DEA doesn't operate that way.

56
00:49:08.571 --> 00:49:10.198
Oh yeah? Then what?!

57
00:49:10.281 --> 00:49:12.450
-Don't be paranoid.
-<i>I want...</i>

58
00:49:12.533 --> 00:49:15.828
I want the DEA names.
you have to prove it to me.

59
00:49:15.912 --> 00:49:18.790
<i>I want their names.
I want their faces.</i>

60
00:49:18.873 --> 00:49:21.000
I want their addresses.
I want them dead...

61
00:49:21.084 --> 00:49:25.963
I want their wives and their kids dead.
and their pets too! Set a trap!

62
00:53:40.468 --> 00:53:42.178
SMILE!

63
00:54:21.342 --> 00:54:23.052
Papito will be proud of you.

64
00:54:23.135 --> 00:54:24.971
That's all I need.

65
00:54:25.846 --> 00:54:28.683
How soon until we're operational?

66
00:54:34.563 --> 00:54:35.564
Look.

67
00:54:39.402 --> 00:54:41.320
Picture of the day.

68
00:54:44.490 --> 00:54:47.368
Look. how handsome!

69
01:17:35.818 --> 01:17:37.320
Good job.

70
01:17:43.743 --> 01:17:45.620
What?

71
01:24:48.709 --> 01:24:50.419
Look. very good!

72
01:24:51.837 --> 01:24:54.298
But why are they still alive?

73
01:25:14.485 --> 01:25:16.445
Kill him. Kill him!

74
01:25:18.614 --> 01:25:20.491
Kill that bastard!

75
01:25:32.002 --> 01:25:34.088
Motherfuckers!

76
01:25:53.440 --> 01:25:55.359
Over here!

77
01:26:03.951 --> 01:26:05.619
Let's go!

78
01:26:22.678 --> 01:26:24.555
Let's take her. We'll trade her.

79
01:26:24.638 --> 01:26:26.348
Go with your sister.

80
01:26:29.727 --> 01:26:31.854
I'll meet you later.
Look after your sister!

81
01:26:31.937 --> 01:26:34.023
-Hurry up!
-Go!

82
01:27:12.937 --> 01:27:14.939
-And Benito?
-He's dead.

83
01:27:25.240 --> 01:27:27.868
Stop!
I'm sick of you. brat!

84
01:27:27.952 --> 01:27:30.412
Are you crazy or what?

85
01:27:31.038 --> 01:27:33.165
Natalia. behind you!
